Feature: Basic Calculator Operations
  As a user
  I want to perform basic calculations
  So that I can get quick mathematical results

  Scenario: Addition of two numbers
    Given I have entered 5 into the calculator
    And I have entered 7 into the calculator
    When I press add
    Then the result should be 12

  Scenario: Subtraction of two numbers
    Given I have entered 10 into the calculator
    And I have entered 4 into the calculator
    When I press subtract
    Then the result should be 6

  Scenario: Division of two numbers
    Given I have entered 15 into the calculator
    And I have entered 3 into the calculator
    When I press divide
    Then the result should be 5

  Scenario: Multiplication of two numbers
    Given I have entered 6 into the calculator
    And I have entered 4 into the calculator
    When I press multiply
    Then the result should be 24

  Scenario: Percentage calculation
    Given I have entered 50 into the calculator
    And I want to calculate 20 percent
    When I press percentage
    Then the result should be 10

  Scenario: Modulus calculation
    Given I have entered 17 into the calculator
    And I have entered 5 into the calculator
    When I press modulus
    Then the result should be 2